全球0800【全球疫情汇总】据新浪实时统计，截至3月22日8点，除中国（包括港澳台地区）以外，海外新冠肺炎累计确诊220113例，死亡9614例，治愈21817例。
According to Sina real-time statistics, as of 8: 00 on March 22, with the exception of China (including Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan), a cumulative total of 220113 new cases of pneumonia were diagnosed, 9,614 deaths were reported and 21,817 cases were cured.
注：新增0表示当天暂未宣布数据。
Note: A new zero indicates that data were not announced for that date.
数据来源：新浪0800【全球新冠肺炎确诊病例超30万，死亡超1.2万】美国约翰斯·霍普金斯大学发布的实时统计数据显示，截至北京时间3月22日4时48分，全球新冠肺炎确诊病例达303001例，超过30万。
According to real-time statistics released by Johns Hopkins University on March 22, 2008, 303,001 new cases of pneumonia have been confirmed worldwide, or more than 300,000, according to real-time statistics released by Johns Hopkins University.
死亡病例累计12762人。
The cumulative number of deaths was 12,762.
0800【为遏制新冠肺炎疫情，全球将近10亿人足不出户】包括政府下“居家令”要求足不出户的6亿人在内，世界各地35个国家有大约9亿多人待在家中。
More than 900 million people remain at home in 35 countries around the world, including the 600 million people the government has ordered them to stay in their homes in order to contain the outbreak.
北美0800【美国确诊新冠肺炎病例累计超过2.4万人，累计病例数居全球第四】截至北京时间22日5时，美国确诊新冠肺炎病例累计24148例，死亡累计285例，治愈171例。
The cumulative number of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in the United States exceeded 24,000, making it the fourth highest in the world. By 0500 hours Beijing time, 24,148 new cases of pneumonia had been confirmed in the United States, with 285 deaths and 171 cases cured.
除中国外，意大利、西班牙、德国及伊朗均破两万。
In addition to China, Italy, Spain, Germany and Iran each broke 20, 000.
美国确诊数已超过伊朗、德国，居全球第四。
The United States has more confirmed than Iran, Germany, ranked fourth in the world.
0800【纽约州成为美国首个新冠肺炎确诊人数过万州】0800【美国调用5500名国民卫队士兵参与抗疫】相关数字有可能随时因疫情而变化。
New York State Becomes the First U.S. State to Have Confirmed New Crown Pneumonia Numbers associated with the U.S. call for 5,500 National Guard soldiers to fight the disease could change over time.
国民卫队的职责将包括个人防护用品培训和样本收集、响应准备、并对卫生和物流系统提供支持等。
The duties of the National Guard will include personal protective equipment training and sample collection, response preparedness, and support to health and logistics systems.
0800【美国副总统将进行新冠病毒检测其办公室职员确诊】当地时间3月21日，美国副总统、白宫应对新冠肺炎疫情特别工作组负责人彭斯表示，他和妻子将进行新冠病毒检测。
US Vice President George W. Bush says he and his wife will be tested for the new crown virus, US Vice President George W. Bush and White House Task Force Leader John Burns said Wednesday.
就在前一天，彭斯的新闻秘书宣布，副总统办公室一名职员的检测结果呈阳性。
Just the day before, Burns' press secretary announced that an employee in the vice president's office had tested positive.
0800【加拿大新冠病毒感染病例增至1146例】欧洲0800【意大利单日新增6557例确诊病例，累计确诊破5万】意大利新增新冠肺炎确诊病例6557例，系单日最大增幅，新增死亡病例793例。
0800 The number of confirmed cases increased to 1146 in Europe [Italy has 6,557 new confirmed cases a day and a cumulative total of 50,000 new cases of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in Italy, representing the largest one-day increase of 793 new deaths.
累计确诊病例增至53578例，累计死亡病例达4825例。
The cumulative number of confirmed cases increased to 53578 and the cumulative number of deaths reached 4,825.
0800【皇马前主席洛伦索-桑斯因新冠肺炎去世享年76岁】0800【俄累计确诊306人已研发出改进型检测系统】0800【法国卫生部长预计未来数日内疫情状况将会恶化】0800【发现新冠肺炎疫情的歌诗达邮轮“炫目”号抵达意大利萨沃纳港】目前船上共有718名旅客和约800名船员，其中84人正处于隔离状态。
Real Madrid president Lorenzo Sands is 76 years old when he died of pneumonia [France's health minister] expects the situation to deteriorate in the next few days The French health minister expects the outbreak to worsen in the next few days.
利古里亚大区民事防护局长詹佩德罗内说，该船已有719名乘客在法国马赛下船，其中有38人确诊感染新冠病毒。
The Director of Civil Defence of the Liguria region, Jan Pedro, said the ship had disembarked 719 passengers in Marseille, France, 38 of whom were confirmed to be infected with the new crown virus.
0800【丹麦新增71例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊1326例】0800【荷兰新增637例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计达3631例】0800【挪威新增211例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊2150例】0800【芬兰现首例新冠肺炎死亡病例累计确诊521例】患者是一名老年人。
cumulative total of 1326 newly diagnosed cases of new crown pneumonia in Denmark total 3,637 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in the Netherlands cumulative total of 2,150 confirmed cases of 211 new cases of new crown pneumonia in Norway The cumulative total number of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in Finland is 521
0800【冰岛新增64例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊473例】亚洲0800【越南将暂停外国人入境】越南共报告94例新冠肺炎确诊病例，其中3月6日以来报告78例，多为境外输入性病例及其接触者。
cumulative total of 473 confirmed new cases of crowns pneumonia in Iceland Asia 0800 [Vietnam will suspend entry of foreigners] Vietnam has reported 94 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia, 78 of which have been reported since March 6.
目前全国已有17例治愈出院。
At present, 17 cases have been cured and discharged.
0800【新冠肺炎恐慌导致斯里兰卡监狱暴动造成1死5伤】截至21日晚，斯里兰卡共确诊新冠肺炎77例。
Sri Lanka has confirmed 77 cases of New Crown Pneumonia (CHP) as of the evening of May 21, 2007.
斯总统府20晚宣布在全国范围内实行外出禁令，目前禁令已延长至24日。
The presidential palace announced a nationwide ban on travel 20 nights, which has now been extended to 24 days.
0800【印度新增32例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊315例】0800【日本国内新冠肺炎确诊病例达1045例累计死亡36例】非洲0800【乌干达确诊首例新冠肺炎病例】患者是一名36岁的乌干达男性，从迪拜搭乘埃塞俄比亚航空飞机抵达乌干达。
cumulative total confirmed cases of 32 new cases of pneumonia in India confirmed 315 cases [total of 1,045 confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia in Japan] Africa 0800 [Uganda] The first confirmed case of New Crown Pneumonia in Uganda is a 36-year-old Ugandan man who arrived in Uganda on an Ethiopian Airlines flight from Dubai.
官方已经追踪到所有搭乘同一班飞机的旅客。
The authorities have tracked down all passengers on the same flight.
0800【加纳出现首例新冠肺炎死亡病例】死者为61岁的黎巴嫩公民，本月19日在加纳被检测出感染新冠病毒。
0800 [Ghana's First Death from Newly Coronary Pneumonia] The 61-year-old Lebanese citizen was tested positive for the new crown virus in Ghana on February 19.
0800【摩洛哥新增10例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊96例】0800【埃及爱资哈尔清真寺停止集体礼拜活动】此次暂停期限为两周。
0800 [Morocco 10 new confirmed cases of pneumonia cumulative confirmed 96 cases] 0800 [Egypt Al-Azhar Mosque to stop the collective worship] This suspension period of two weeks.
埃及卫生与人口部21日发表声明称，埃及新增新冠肺炎确诊病例9例累计确诊294例。
Egypt's Ministry of Health and Population issued a statement on the 21, Egypt's new crown pneumonia confirmed 9 cases cumulatively confirmed 294.
中东0800【以色列驻纽约领事馆一工作人员确诊患有新冠肺炎】这名工人自我感觉身体状态稳定，已被隔离治疗。
Middle East 0800 [New Crown Pneumonia confirmed by a staff member of the Israeli Consulate in New York] The worker feels in stable health and has been treated in isolation.
目前以色列本土新冠肺炎确诊病例为883例，这一数字正在快速增加中。
There are now 883 confirmed cases of indigenous pneumonia in Israel, a number that is rapidly increasing.
0800【黎巴嫩总理：安全部队将介入全国强制性封锁】黎巴嫩进入疫情的暴发期，过去24小时内确诊人数增加67人，是自疫情在黎巴嫩出现以来单日人数增长最多的一天。
0800 [Prime Minister of Lebanon: Security forces will intervene in the country's mandatory blockade] Lebanon enters an outbreak, with an increase of 67 confirmed cases over the past 24 hours, the largest increase in a single day since the outbreak began in Lebanon.
当地时间21日晚，黎巴嫩总理哈桑·迪亚卜发表电视讲话，表示黎巴嫩安全部队将会介入并采取强制措施，禁止居民外出和集会。
On the evening of 21 local time, Lebanese Prime Minister Hassan Diab made a televised speech in which he said the Lebanese security forces would intervene and take coercive measures to ban residents from travelling and gathering.
0800【土耳其新增新冠肺炎确诊病例277例累计确诊947例】0800【土耳其内政部：65岁以上老人不得离开住所】土耳其卫生部长称，死亡的9例均为老年人。
0800 [277 Cases of Confirmed New Crown Pneumonia in Turkey Cumulatively Confirmed 947 Cases] 0800 [Ministry of Interior of Turkey: No one over 65 years of age is allowed to leave their homes] The Turkish Minister of Health states that 9 of the deaths were old people.
0800【卡塔尔采取严厉措施防止新冠肺炎疫情扩散】从即日起以法律形式禁止一切形式的集会，包括但不限于海滨大道、公园、公共海滩、社交集会等地点和场合。
0800 [Qatar takes stringent measures to prevent the spread of the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic] Effective from this date, all forms of assembly, including but not limited to seaside roads, parks, public beaches, social gatherings, etc., are prohibited by law.
违反相关规定的人将面临被逮捕的风险，所有商家也都禁止营业，但外卖业务不受相应影响。
Those who violate the relevant regulations are at risk of arrest and all businesses are prohibited from operating, but the take-out business is not affected accordingly.
该决定初步暂定两周，随后将对情况进行评估后决定是否延长。
The decision is tentatively tentatively scheduled for two weeks and will be followed by an assessment of the situation and a decision on whether to extend it.
0800【伊拉克新增6例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊214例】大洋洲0800【澳总理：大多数病例源于美国抗疫举措步步升级】据莫里森政府预计，澳新冠肺炎疫情最坏可能导致近15万人死亡。
Australia: Most cases stem from the escalation of the U.S. Plague Initiative. The Morrison government expects the worst possible death toll from the New Zealand Crown Pneumonia epidemic to be nearly 150,000.
拉美0800【巴西累计确诊1128例新冠肺炎病例圣保罗等城市开建“方舱”医院】目前政府正在加快检测试剂的生产，本周末政府将分发1万套检测试剂给各州的检测机构，接下来还将再分发500万套快速检测试剂，以提高检测量。
Latin America 0800 [Brazil Cumulatively Identifies 1128 Cases of New Crown Pneumonia in Sao Paulo and other cities) The government is speeding up the production of testing reagents. The government will distribute 10,000 test reagents to state testing facilities by the end of this week, followed by another 5 million rapid-detection reagents to boost testing.
